race.comment: TAHITIAN GIRL (4) is having her first run over this longer distance. Excellent winning strike-rate off this box. Looks suited and should go close. COOL IT (7) was responsible for a modest effort most recently when fifth at Q Lakeside over 642m behind Goldstar Prada (36.87) in a Restricted WIN. Was in the money prior to that. Key player if finds best. LITTLE LIES (6) turned spotting a big start finishing fourth (35.33) last time in a Grade 5 at this track. Form from her last run is proving strong. Cannot be taken lightly. LUMBY (3) has strong credentials from this draw.
